&lt;h2&gt;Role Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Operations &amp;amp; Systems Analyst is the connective tissue of Game Plan Tech&#39;s internal operations. This person owns our internal tool ecosystem, ensures our data is accurate and trustworthy, maintains our company knowledge base in Notion, and delivers dashboards and reports that help leadership make informed decisions. This is a high-visibility, high-impact individual contributor role that sits at the intersection of operations, data, and technology.&lt;/p&gt;
